### ============================================================
### Dev Seed — bootstrap local database with venues & sources
###
### Run all requests in this file sequentially (▶▶ "Run All")
### after starting the importer with a fresh database.
### Requests are idempotent-safe: duplicates will return 409.
###
### Import triggers are asynchronous: each returns 202 Accepted immediately and the
### import runs in the background, so events keep landing for up to ~a minute after the
### run finishes. Poll `GET /api/admin/event-sources` to watch each source's status.
###
### Sources (alphabetical):
###   Astra Kulturhaus     — https://www.astra-berlin.de/
###   Badehaus             — https://badehaus-berlin.com/events/
###   Bi Nuu               — https://binuu.de/de/events
###   Cassiopeia           — https://cassiopeia-berlin.de/club
###   Duncker Club         — https://www.dunckerclub.de/start.html
###   Festsaal Kreuzberg   — https://festsaal-kreuzberg.de/de/programm/ (Wagtail CMS JSON API)
###   Frannz Club          — https://frannz.eu/
###   Gretchen             — https://www.gretchen-club.de/
###   Lido                 — https://www.lido-berlin.de/
###   Madame Claude        — https://madameclaude.de/ (WordPress `event` REST API, ACF-backed)
###   Neue Zukunft         — https://neue-zukunft.org/ (Elfsight Event Calendar widget JSON API)
###   Privatclub           — https://privatclub-berlin.de/
###   Roadrunner's Paradise — http://www.roadrunners-paradise.de/programm.html
###   Schokoladen          — https://www.schokoladen-mitte.de/
###   SO36                 — https://www.so36.com/tickets
### ============================================================

### ————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————
### Astra Kulturhaus (Revaler Str. 99, Berlin-Friedrichshain — RAW-Gelände)
### ————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————

### --- Create Astra Kulturhaus venue ---
POST {{importer-host}}/api/admin/venues
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Astra Kulturhaus",
    "address": "Revaler Str. 99",
    "city": "Berlin",
    "postalCode": "10245",
    "district": "friedrichshain-kreuzberg",
    "latitude": 52.50724,
    "longitude": 13.45180,
    "websiteUrl": "https://www.astra-berlin.de"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("astra_venue_id", response.body.id);
    client.test("Astra Kulturhaus venue created", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 201, "Expected 201 but got " + response.status);
    });
%}

### --- Create Astra Kulturhaus event source ---
# Links the venue to the AstraWebsiteImporter.
# The sourceType "ASTRA" matches EventSource.ASTRA.
# NOTE: the URL is the homepage `/` (the program); `/events` is the past archive.
POST {{importer-host}}/api/admin/event-sources
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "venueId": {{astra_venue_id}},
    "name": "Astra Kulturhaus",
    "url": "https://www.astra-berlin.de/",
    "sourceType": "ASTRA",
    "enabled": true,
    "importIntervalMinutes": 1440,
    "maxRetries": 3
}

> {%
    client.test("Astra Kulturhaus event source created", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 201, "Expected 201 but got " + response.status);
    });
%}

### --- Trigger initial Astra Kulturhaus import ---
POST {{importer-host}}/api/admin/event-sources/astra-kulturhaus/import
Accept: application/json

> {%
    client.test("Astra Kulturhaus import triggered", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 202, "Expected 202 but got " + response.status);
    });
%}

